SUMMARY:Same Hike But Backwards!
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\n**Meetup Point: 10443 Nassaga
 weya-Esquesing Halton Hills**\n**Coordinates: 43.556893\, -79.984225**\n**
 PS: Please follow the address and coordinates. Not the pin.**\n\nHey All: 
 Because we liked today's hike so much we are going back next week and comi
 ng in from the opposite direction. It's a large area so we want to do it a
 gain from the opposite side - there are lots of side trails.\nThere are so
 me single track side trails that are more moderate or hard as well\, and t
 he route is a great option. Overall\, this is a beautiful place with lots 
 of trail options whether you want to have a leisurely walk or challenge yo
 urself a bit.\nYou can expect rocks\, flat areas and forest. Its a lovely 
 mixed bag!\nIts a different point of view!\nThis is a 15km hike. If your u
 p for it we can always make it a longer hike. It might be muddy so wear wa
 terproof boots and hiking poles are helpful. We will be stopping for lunch
  at 1pm so bring lots of water and nibbles.\nPS: A note on car pooling. Pl
 ease offer a ride to someone. Many people want to come and can't find ride
 s. This is part of the BOOTS Community. We help each other out. Also\, you
  can ask for gas money remember your passenger is not there to fill your t
 ank but to contribute to gas. $10. to $15\, is the max you should ask. If 
 there are multiple people\, $10\, per person.
