BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: These Boots Are Made for Hiking
UID:event_313749628@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260411T025611Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260418T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260419T170000
SUMMARY:Time to learn New Skills - Trecking Training  - Two Day Hike with 
 Full Gear
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\nZoom Call: Monday March 23\, 
 7:30pm\n\nMeet up Point: 6700 Salmon Lake Road\, Sydenham\, ON K0H 2T0\, C
 anada\n**Two days...sat and sun**\n**Fee for Trekking Training: $99.**\n\n
 We have a secret and an agenda. We want you (and all our members) out Trek
 ing. At least once. Don't give up your Sunday hikes\, but hey it's time to
  up your hiking game!\nWhich is why we are offering skills training for fu
 ture trekkers so they can join in on trekking adventures outside of Ontari
 o.\nThere is a lot to learn to prepare for a multi day trekk\, and we want
  you to be prepared. It is not just knowing what equipment to buy\, how mu
 ch to carry\, tent set up\, it's also food prep\, attitude\, and emergency
  skills and so much more!\nSo\, in order for you to ensure you have a safe
  and the very BEST trekking experience we are offering a day in Big Salmon
  Lake.\n**Experienced Boots Trekkers feel free to hop in and show them how
  it's done!**\nWe will cover in one weekend -\n\n* your weighted pack\n* p
 ack pacing\n* water filtering\n* trail etiquette\n* safety\n* equipment mu
 st haves\n* first aid\n* attittude adjustment\n* fire starting\n* navigati
 on\n* ...and more
