SUMMARY:Niagara Falls! Here we come by BIKE!
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\n**MEETUP POINT: Burlington Go
  Station**\nJoin us for an all day bike riding event from Burlington Go to
  Niagara Falls and back. Total length of ride is 100km\, so obviously this
  is not a beginner ride.\nPlease ensure you are bike ready so take your bi
 ke out and start practicing in the spring to get yourself in good shape fo
 r this ride! I will post some practice rides starting in May and June\nNo 
 commuter bikes please.\nYou will catch the go train nearest you which is $
 10. and take it to the Burlington Go station which we will all meet -time 
 to be confirmed\, and begin our ride from there.\nLunch will be in Niagara
  Falls. Ensure you bring power snacks and water with lots of electrolytes!
 \n[https://ridewithgps.com/routes/53737914](https://ridewithgps.com/routes
 /53737914)
