SUMMARY:Come to BC With Us!
DESCRIPTION:These Boots Are Made for Hiking\nGrab your Hiking boots and po
 les and come to BC with us!\nThis is a week of day hikes - some challengin
 g and some just downright beautiful. We will be day hiking for 7 days begi
 nning in Vancouver heading to Tofino Beach then back to Vancouver.\nThe it
 inerary looks something like this:\n\n1\\. Day 1\\- Sat\\. August 8 – Va
 ncouver\nStay overnight\n2\\. Day 2 – Sun\\. August 9 – 9am departure 
 \\- Day trip to Squamish to hike Squamish Valley/ or Garibaldi national pa
 rk\n3\\. Day 3 – Mon\\. August 10 – Leave at 7am to catch the Horsehoe
  Bay Ferry Terminal to Nanaimo\nHike Neck Point Lake in the afternoon/ sta
 y at painted Turtle Guesthouse if available\n4\\. Day 4 – Tues\\. August
  11 – 7am departure to Ucuelet \\-along the way we stop at the old fores
 t and falls at Cathedral Grove\\. We might check out Mount Benson given ti
 me constraints\\.\nStay at C&N Backpackers Hostel depending on availabilit
 y\n5\\. Day 5 \\-Wed\\. August 12 – 9am departure – Hike Wild Pacific 
 Trail and swim at Florencia Bay\n6\\. Day 6 – Thurs\\. August 13 – 10a
 m departure \\- Pacific Rim to Tofino – Rain forest trail\\\, Long Beach
  and explore the town – optional tour if interested\n7\\. Day 7 – Fri\
 \. August 14 – 7 am departure – Catch the water taxi – 30\\.return p
 lus 10\\. Park fee\\. Hike Lone Cone Trail then head back to Vancouver\n8\
 \. Day 8 – Sat\\. Aug 15 – Head back to Vancouver\n9\\. Day 9 \\- Sun\
 \. Aug 16 – Return to Toronto\nJoin our zoom call Wed. April 22\nsherry 
 bagnato is inviting you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.\nTopic: BC Here we co
 me!\nTime: Apr 22\, 2026 07:30 PM Eastern Time (US and Canada)\nJoin the Z
 oom Meeting for details!\nhttps://us05web.zoom.us/j/82687571918?pwd=dJniSd
 1V70Ai6miGXG2YDpo1gHcPNN.1\nMeeting ID: 826 8757 1918\nPasscode: KEcQ6D\nJ
 oin instructions\nhttps://us05web.zoom.us/meetings/82687571918/invitations
 ?signature=uTr6fHNG9vPac2AOb1mrkxZsXUq2KFiRTiCw5fQfaXo
